snippet.title: NEW 2025 RHYTHM GAME - 60 BPM is releasing next week!!! Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready to feel the rhythm with 60 BPM - an electrifying rhythm game! With stunning levels, addictive tracks, and thrilling visuals, this adventure will keep you on your toes. Stay tuned - the beat drops soon!

Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3222860/60_BPM
